						 <p>First off: Thank you and I am glad you enjoyed it.</p> <p>As for the criticism: I guess you can never get enough crit :D The only thing I will leave is the tooth as it was probably still covered with blood and or saliva which obviously both contain DNA. The fight has a specific line of events which I do not want to obscure too much. Thank you again though! This was very helpful.</p> 
