						 <p>After 5 Months of work and absence and work on this, it is finally done.</p> <p>Big thanks for conceptual and writing critique and help goes to: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/acidninjacake" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4691694&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="acidninjacake" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4691694)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/acidninjacake" >acidninjacake</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" >Mortos</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3118444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="Pedantique" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3118444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" >Pedantique</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5012224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="AthosNetwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5012224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" >AthosNetwork</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" >ManyMeats</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcaroll" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3828846&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="DrCaroll" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3828846)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drcaroll" >DrCaroll</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span></p> <p>(Phew what a list, hope I got everyone. Could not have made it without you guys!)</p> <p>And <strong>special thanks</strong> to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lord-of-laugh" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2916583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="Lord_of_Laugh" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2916583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lord-of-laugh" >Lord_of_Laugh</a></span> for photoshopping the image of the kitchen. (Minor edits by me.)</p> <p>I also want to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pxdnbluesoul" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414125&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564862191" alt="pxdnbluesoul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414125)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pxdnbluesoul" >pxdnbluesoul</a></span> for featuring this article on the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mx9FzpzPN1o&amp;t=5s">SCP Café Podcast Episode 20</a>!</p> <p>The idea for this came to me on the day after new years eve, laying in bed in a friends house.<br /> I looked up at their wall full of travel photographs and thought to myself &quot;What if one of these pictures just&#8230; overtook the others?&quot; And that was that. Feels good to have my first article be my favourite kind: A thing what does a thing, that hopefully works!</p> <p>This will probably not be the last you will read of me! Hope you enjoyed!</p> <p>ᵗʰᶦˢ ˢᶜᵖ ᶦˢ ᵈᵉᵈᶦᶜᵃᵗᵉᵈ ᵗᵒ ˣᶦˡᵃˢᶜʳᵒʷᵉ</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">All&nbsp;dem&nbsp;links</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>&quot;Kitchen&quot; is comprised of: 1. <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/roland/230439770">https://www.flickr.com/photos/roland/230439770</a> 2. <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/louisephotography/4649041863">https://www.flickr.com/photos/louisephotography/4649041863</a> 3. <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dirty_Room_2_2013-06-14.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dirty_Room_2_2013-06-14.jpg</a> 4. <a href="https://www.maxpixel.net/Paper-Sound-Round-Pile-Phonograph-Record-45-Rpm-3173272">https://www.maxpixel.net/Paper-Sound-Round-Pile-Phonograph-Record-45-Rpm-3173272</a><br /> &quot;SCP-XXXX-A-1&quot; is cropped from:<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/119886413@N05/19462410472/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/119886413@N05/19462410472/</a><br /> &quot;SCP-XXXX-A-2&quot; is cropped from:<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/auxesis/3206242822/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/auxesis/3206242822/</a><br /> &quot;SCP-XXXX-A-3&quot; is cropped from:<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/raselased/3745574352/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/raselased/3745574352/</a><br /> &quot;SCP-XXXX-A-4&quot; is cropped from:<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/httpoldmaisonblogspotcom/8010205337/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/httpoldmaisonblogspotcom/8010205337/</a><br /> &quot;SCP-XXXX-A-5&quot; is cropped from:<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/erikjacobs/9732225883/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/erikjacobs/9732225883/</a></p> </div> </div> </div> <p>If you have enjoyed this, here is more of my stuff <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/poi-3181-198-file">http://www.scp-wiki.net/poi-3181-198-file</a>!</p> 
